headline: Behr Paint Company Announces 2026 Color of the Year: Hidden Gem - A Smoky Jade That Embodies Understated Elegance and Timeless Sophistication
summary: Today, Behr Paint Company unveils Hidden Gem (N430-6A) as its 2026 Color of the Year—a smoky jade that uncovers exceptional beauty in every space. This dynamic blend of blue and green creates environments that feel both grounded and energizing—striking a redefined balance as a one-of-a-kind color.
